title: Liquid damaged 820-02020 stuck at 5v.  PPBUS_AON pulsing to 12.3v
message:
UD560 looked heavily corroded so I have removed, cleaned and reseated.
There is nothing powering it, pin 6 voltage P3V3_S2SW_SNS is zero.
I can see PPBUS_AON pulsing to 12.3volts
U5200 ISL9240HI and surrounding components reflowed to no effect.
